  <compounddef id="conceptargs_23" kind="concept">
    <compoundname>args/3</compoundname>
    <initializer>template&lt;&gt;
concept args/3 =     </initializer>
    <briefdescription>
<para><bold>args</bold>( +_Index_, +_ListOfTerms_ , -_ListOfArgs_ ) </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Succeeds if <emphasis>ListOfArgs</emphasis> unifies with the application of <ref refid="classgenarg_23" kindref="compound">genarg/3</ref> to every element of <emphasis>ListOfTerms</emphasis></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>It corresponds to calling <ref refid="classmaplist_23" kindref="compound">maplist/3</ref> on <ref refid="classgenarg_23" kindref="compound">genarg/3</ref> : <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight><highlight class="normal">args(<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">I</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">Ts</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">As</highlight><highlight class="normal">)<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">:-</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight><highlight class="normal">maplist(<sp/>genarg(</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">I</highlight><highlight class="normal">),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">Ts</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">As</highlight><highlight class="normal">)</highlight><highlight class="keyword">.</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Notice that unification allows <emphasis>ListOfArgs</emphasis> to be bound, eg:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keyword">?-</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight><highlight class="normal">args(</highlight><highlight class="vhldigit">1</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>[</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X1</highlight><highlight class="keyword">+</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">Y1</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X2</highlight><highlight class="keyword">-</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">Y2</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X3</highlight><highlight class="keyword">*</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">Y3</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X4</highlight><highlight class="keyword">/</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">Y4</highlight><highlight class="normal">],<sp/>[</highlight><highlight class="vhldigit">1</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="vhldigit">1</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="vhldigit">1</highlight><highlight class="normal">,</highlight><highlight class="vhldigit">1</highlight><highlight class="normal">]).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X1</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">=</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X2</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">=</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X3</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">=</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="charliteral">X4</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">=</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="vhldigit">1</highlight><highlight class="keyword">.</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
    <location file="library/arg.yap" line="2" column="1"/>
  </compounddef>
